( sighs )

00:32.306 --> 00:33.680
Come on.

00:33.680 --> 00:37.139
I can't look at that.
Take it away.

00:37.139 --> 00:39.473
- ( window opens )
- Hey, I'm trying to work.

00:39.473 --> 00:41.056
Sorry,
what's your problem?

00:41.056 --> 00:43.805
No one wants to see this.
It's very disturbing.

00:43.805 --> 00:45.473
Two people aren't
allowed to be happy?

00:45.473 --> 00:46.930
Well, you're allowed
to be happy,

00:46.930 --> 00:48.764
