24:41.598 --> 24:42.680
Uh, I guess so.

24:42.680 --> 24:43.930
Okay, I'll see you then.

24:43.930 --> 24:46.097
All right.
Goodbye.

24:46.097 --> 24:50.598
So, uh, Larry, again,
we're very happy you came in,
talked to us about Eddie.

24:50.598 --> 24:53.598
I think things, um--
I think look pretty good.

24:53.598 --> 24:54.930
We're very, uh...

24:56.473 --> 24:58.431
Could my handyman
and his family

24:58.431 --> 25:00.598
use your pool
on Saturday?

25:06.598 --> 25:09.056
( whispering,
chuckling )

25:14.473 --> 25:16.348
- Hi.
- Hey.

25:16.348 --> 25:17.805
- Same table.
- Is it?

25:17.805 --> 25:19.972
- Champagne.
- Oh.

25:19.972 --> 25:22.014
- This time we'll drink it.
- ( nervous chuckling )

25:22.014 --> 25:23.722
- What's the matter?
- ( stammering )

25:23.722 --> 25:27.473
I just got off the phone
with the Pemberton Academy.

25:27.473 --> 25:28.805
What'd they say?

25:28.805 --> 25:30.014
Eddie didn't get in.

25:30.014 --> 25:31.473
- He didn't get in?
- No.

25:31.473 --> 25:32.889
Why?

25:32.889 --> 25:34.306
Because
of the condition

25:34.306 --> 25:36.722
that your handyman
and his family

25:36.722 --> 25:38.930
left the Pemberton Academy
pool.

25:38.930 --> 25:40.473
What?
What's the condition?

25:40.473 --> 25:42.014
Befouled.

25:42.014 --> 25:44.264
Little Cesar
befouled the pool?

25:44.264 --> 25:45.306
Why would you
send them there?

25:45.306 --> 25:46.972
Of all the pools
in California?

25:46.972 --> 25:48.972
I don't know,
'cause Little Cesar
wanted to use a pool!

25:48.972 --> 25:50.639
I couldn't-- I couldn't
refuse Little Cesar.

25:50.639 --> 25:52.264
Why do they have
to use a pool at all?

25:52.264 --> 25:54.222
Cesar flipped
the tip on me
and, you know,

25:54.222 --> 25:55.972
he wouldn't take the tip,
so I was obligated to!

25:55.972 --> 25:57.181
- Hi!
- Hello!

25:57.181 --> 25:59.139
More obligated
than to-- hi!

25:59.139 --> 26:01.222
- Hi.
- How are you?

26:01.222 --> 26:02.889
What a day!

26:02.889 --> 26:04.680
We just came back
from Catalina.

26:04.680 --> 26:07.431
- Oh, heard that's beautiful.
- What a cruise!

26:07.431 --> 26:09.306
- Dolphins!
- Great boat, beautiful.

26:09.306 --> 26:10.847
- Magnificent.
- I think I got too much sun.

26:10.847 --> 26:12.222
Funkhouser:
How are you guys doing?

26:12.222 --> 26:16.264
Gosh, I am so sorry,
but I think I have to go.

26:16.264 --> 26:19.639
- Oh, no.
- We just had a "go home"
argument, and I have to go.

26:19.639 --> 26:22.764
Oh, no, no, no.
Don't do that!
No, don't do that!

26:22.764 --> 26:25.473
