I'm not gonna be able
to rally for today.

26:25.473 --> 26:27.014
- Yeah.
- Thank you.
You understand.

26:27.014 --> 26:28.847
- Thanks for trying.
- Oh, no. I'm sorry, no.

26:28.847 --> 26:31.181
I'll see you,
maybe, again,
but who can say?

26:31.181 --> 26:34.680
- I might not.
- No, I'm so-- ah!
Ah, I'm sorry!

26:34.680 --> 26:36.389
Enjoy the champagne.

26:36.389 --> 26:39.097
- I'm sorry! Ah!
- Here we go.

26:39.097 --> 26:40.389
( cork pops )

26:44.056 --> 26:45.556
( tires screech )

26:47.598 --> 26:49.181
Oh!

26:55.556 --> 26:58.514
Mr. David, get in.

26:58.514 --> 27:01.348
Get-- get in the car?
What, where-- where
are we going?

27:01.348 --> 27:03.889
I haven't even
had-- had brunch yet.

27:03.889 --> 27:05.348
Get in.

27:05.348 --> 27:06.722
Okay.

27:08.222 --> 27:10.264
Oh, my God.

27:10.264 --> 27:11.181
Go.

27:14.722 --> 27:17.639
Morsi:
There was no reason for me
to get to the back of the line.

27:17.639 --> 27:19.972
As I said,
I had already waited,

27:19.972 --> 27:26.181
and those brunch buffet lines
are interminable.

27:26.181 --> 27:28.389
Yes, I am familiar

27:28.389 --> 27:30.764
because
they cook the eggs
while you wait.

27:30.764 --> 27:32.181
( muftis agree )

27:32.181 --> 27:36.097
And all I wanted--
just a little bit more
home fries.

27:36.097 --> 27:37.680
Ah, yes, home fries.

27:37.680 --> 27:39.764
A nice compliment
to the eggs.

27:39.764 --> 27:41.431
With ketchup?

27:41.431 --> 27:43.181
( chuckles )
Yes, of course.

27:43.181 --> 27:46.847
( chattering in Arabic )

27:46.847 --> 27:50.181
So it seems wrong to wait
15 minutes just for that.

27:50.181 --> 27:52.473
Yes, of course.
Why even get them?

27:52.473 --> 27:55.722
Exactly.
So I took a chance.

27:55.722 --> 27:57.097
But the outcry

27:57.097 --> 28:00.431
was unlike anything
you could ever imagine.

28:00.431 --> 28:02.473
You are perceived
as a cutter.

28:02.473 --> 28:05.222
There's nothing Americans
hate more than a cutter.

28:05.222 --> 28:06.473
- He is right.
- It's true.

28:06.473 --> 28:10.556
You're right, Mufti.
I was humiliated.

28:10.556 --> 28:12.722
But this man...

28:12.722 --> 28:14.805
he rose
to my defense.

28:14.805 --> 28:17.431
He said I have
every right

28:17.431 --> 28:20.222
to get seconds
without waiting.

28:20.222 --> 28:22.930
He was forceful,
passionate,

28:22.930 --> 28:25.389
and courageous.

28:25.389 --> 28:28.639
When the American
blood sugar gets low,

28:28.639 --> 28:30.598
they turn into animals.

28:30.598 --> 28:32.097
It's very intimidating.

28:32.097 --> 28:33.764
- True.
- I have seen it.

28:33.764 --> 28:36.014
Morsi:
Not this man.

28:36.014 --> 28:37.639
It was something to see.

28:37.639 --> 28:41.222
And that's why
I come before you

28:41.222 --> 28:45.556
to beg you
to reevaluate his case.

28:45.556 --> 28:49.972
I have read the report
of your investigation
with great interest.

28:49.972 --> 28:53.014
However, there are
many things in his past

28:53.014 --> 28:55.930
which contradict his behavior
in the restaurant.

28:55.930 --> 29:01.598
For example,
this business about not
giving out candy on Halloween.

29:01.598 --> 29:03.847
Surely that cannot
be justified.

29:03.847 --> 29:07.805
With all due respect,
he did give out candies.

29:07.805 --> 29:11.181
But the girls in question,
they were teenagers.

29:11.181 --> 29:13.014
Much too old
to be tricking.

29:13.014 --> 29:15.514
Tricking or treating?

29:15.514 --> 29:17.764
This is all
so very confusing.

29:17.764 --> 29:19.598
Well, you play tricks

29:19.598 --> 29:22.598
if you don't get the treat,
is my understanding.

29:22.598 --> 29:25.264
- ( muftis murmuring )
- Yes, I believe
that is correct.

29:25.264 --> 29:26.972
That is confusing.

29:26.972 --> 29:28.514
But the girls
were 16.

29:28.514 --> 29:31.722
You don't trick
when you're 16.

29:31.722 --> 29:35.222
That's not tricking,
that's stealing.

29:35.222 --> 29:37.181
By denying
them candy,

29:37.181 --> 29:39.722
he was teaching them
a lesson.

29:39.722 --> 29:41.680
- ( muftis agreeing )
- Yes.

29:41.680 --> 29:44.389
- ( all murmuring )
- I see your point.

29:44.389 --> 29:46.930
Ah, very good.
Very good.

29:46.930 --> 29:49.556
- ( speaking Arabic )
- Pass the plates, gentlemen.

29:49.556 --> 29:52.722
- Falafel. Yes, falafel.
- Mufti #2: Another falafel
over here.

29:52.722 --> 29:54.056
- Kabob.
- Kabob for me.

29:54.056 --> 29:57.348
- Onion rings. Yes.
- Ah, french fries.

29:57.348 --> 30:01.722
Mufti:
But what about
his values?

30:01.722 --> 30:03.722
His lust knows no bounds.

30:03.722 --> 30:07.348
He will have
sexual congress
with anyone, anytime.

30:07.348 --> 30:09.930
