30:09.930 --> 30:12.389
- ( muftis murmuring )
- What? Is this true?

30:12.389 --> 30:14.181
This is so?

30:14.181 --> 30:15.972
You know this
for a fact?

30:15.972 --> 30:17.473
Twice.

30:17.473 --> 30:18.722
- Twice!
- ( muftis murmuring )

30:18.722 --> 30:20.181
A Muslim woman?

30:20.181 --> 30:21.264
Morsi:
Yes, Mufti,

30:21.264 --> 30:22.556
