30:22.556 --> 30:24.431
( murmuring )

30:24.431 --> 30:26.722
Mufti:
Very interesting.

30:26.722 --> 30:29.431
This is new information.

30:29.431 --> 30:32.306
I will personally
contact the ayatollah

30:32.306 --> 30:35.139
and let him know
what we have learned.

30:36.598 --> 30:39.097
I can say
without reservation

30:39.097 --> 30:42.389
that he will rescind
the fatwa.

30:42.389 --> 30:46.930
- You are free to go.
- Thank you, "Moofti"!
"Muff-ti"!

30:46.930 --> 30:48.805
Thank you all,
moo-mooftis and muff-tis.

30:48.805 --> 30:50.306
Is it "muff-ti"
or "moofti"?

30:50.306 --> 30:51.473
"Moofti."

30:51.473 --> 30:53.181
- "Moovti."
- "Moovti."

30:53.181 --> 30:54.556
Thank you, "Moovtis."

30:54.556 --> 30:57.097
Thank you so--
but what about the musical?

30:57.097 --> 30:58.930
Um, the musical
"Fatwa!"?

30:58.930 --> 31:01.930
I will say this
about the musical...

31:03.431 --> 31:05.847
If you can get
Lin-Manuel Miranda,

31:05.847 --> 31:07.473
you know,
from "Hamilton"...

31:07.473 --> 31:10.222
- ( muftis agreeing )
- Yes! I love "Hamilton"!

31:10.222 --> 31:13.056
If you can get
Lin-Manuel Miranda to star,

31:13.056 --> 31:14.598
you can proceed
with the musical.

31:14.598 --> 31:15.889
( stammering )
How am I gonna
get Lin-Manuel?

31:15.889 --> 31:17.680
He-- he's got
his own stuff he does.

31:17.680 --> 31:19.139
- He's not gonna be in this.
- ( bottle squirting )

31:19.139 --> 31:20.972
What are you doing
with the ketchup?

31:20.972 --> 31:22.556
