- ( chattering )

31:48.139 --> 31:49.556
Thank you.

32:01.639 --> 32:03.014
Huh. Okay.

32:03.014 --> 32:06.014
- Driver: Here you are.
- All right. Very nice.

32:06.014 --> 32:08.097
- All right.
- Thank you so much
for everything.

32:08.097 --> 32:10.348
