32:16.722 --> 32:18.722
- Take the money. What?
- No. You are going
to embar--

32:18.722 --> 32:20.222
- You are offending me.
- You're offending me!

32:20.222 --> 32:22.222
( arguing )

32:22.222 --> 32:23.972
- I'm not taking--
- Look. Yeah, take it.

32:23.972 --> 32:26.389
- I don't want it. Yeah.
- No! Take it back!

32:26.389 --> 32:27.722
I don't want it!

32:27.722 --> 32:29.889
I can't take that
from you, sir!

32:29.889 --> 32:31.473
I will not take
this tip, okay?

32:31.473 --> 32:32.598
Take the money!

32:32.598 --> 32:34.514
You ain't gonna
flip a tip on me!

32:34.514 --> 32:37.389
